Package: MMV
Type: Package
Title: Visualization Toolkit for Water Maze and Minefield Tasks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Haoliang",
             family = "Zhu",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "haoliang@example.com"))
Description: R-first plotting toolkit for behavior trajectory visualization.
    It supports two independent tasks (water maze and minefield) with a
    common CSV schema, automatic plotting, batch rendering, thisplot-aware
    themes, and optional Python extension hooks via
    reticulate.
